### 2. `manifest.json` (The Web Manifest File)
*This configuration enables standard app behavior, giving the PWA its app name and background colors.*

```json
{
  "name": "Bokmal CEFR Scale Builder",
  "short_name": "BokmalPWA",
  "start_url": "index.html",
  "display": "standalone",
  "background_color": "#f4f6f9",
  "theme-color": "#002f6c",
  "orientation": "portrait-primary",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "https://flaticon.com",
      "type": "image/png",
      "sizes": "512x512",
      "purpose": "any maskable"
    }
  ]
}